# MCR 420: Materials Counts (3) - Flattened Formats

**Date Posted:** June 22, 2026

## Overview

This query is the third of four queries used to support annual materials count reporting. It creates a flattened version of the primary formats table generated by MCR 419.

The primary formats table contains array-based fields that support multiple format assignments. This query converts those arrays into a structure that is easier to aggregate, summarize, and report.

## Notes

- Each format assignment is represented as an individual row.
- This structure supports simpler SQL aggregation and reporting.
- The flattened table is used directly by MCR 421.

## Workflow

```text
MCR 418 (Data Prep)
        ↓
MCR 419 (Primary Formats)
        ↓
MCR 420 (Flattened Formats)
        ↓
MCR 421 (Materials Counts)
